name: Vintage, Brand New Playmaxx Turbo Bumble Bee Yo-Yo
description:
PLAYMAXX TURBO BUMBLE BEE® Yo-Yo
The ProYo classic is here with the PLAYMAXX logo!

If you're looking for one of the most classic loopers around, you've gotta try a TURBO Bumblebee yoyo.

Using Duncan's Brake Pad response, a long spinning ball bearing, and the classic modified standard shape, The Bumblebee yo-yo is a sure fire way to kick start your two-handed looping tricks (2A).

This item is new/unused WITHOUT packaging. comes as shown, with a "bee string" attached.

name: Duncan Butterfly Yo-Yo
description:
Perhaps one of the most popular yo-yos of all time, the Duncan Butterfly yo-yo paved the way to a new era of yo-yo shapes!
The Duncan Butterfly yo-yo, first released in the 1950's, made it easier for people to land and perform more complex string tricks with its wide inward-tapered shape and rim concentrated weight. Even now, string trick yo-yos use a similar "butterfly" shape. This is the ORIGINAL Duncan Butterfly yo-yo, with a metal fixed axle and non-modular halves. It's a great yo-yo to start learning tricks, and a great stress reliever as well!

Relive your memories with the Duncan Butterfly Yo-Yo!

name: Duncan RAPTOR Yo-Yo
description:
There is a lot to get excited about with Duncan's new release of the Raptor! A great aluminum yo-yo for intermediate yo-yo player looking to get advanced!

The Raptor is an all aluminum yo-yo with a comfortable shape and a design that makes it fast and agile on the string. Duncan took their time with this one and it truly shows. Duncan Crew member Tomas Bubak used it in his winning freestyle at the 2011 European Yo-Yo Contest!

It includes side caps to give it a different look and overall feel if you choose to use them!

Features a nice wide gap with a Size C (.250 x .500 x .187) bearing.

PLEASE NOTE....THIS YO-YO IS NON-REPSONSIVE! If you are unsure of what this means, you will most likely NOT be able to use it!

Full warranty from Duncan Toys, Inc.

name: Duncan Yo-Yo Starter Set
description:
Check this out! a BRAND NEW, NEVER USED Duncan Yo-Yo Starter Set! You'll get ALL THIS!

    * Duncan "Reflex" Yo-Yo: Auto-Return Technology! The special "Auto-Return" technology brings the yo-yo back to your hand automatically. It has a high speed axle design and lightweight body for ultra fast play. Has an aerodynamic rim-weighted shape. The Reflex is great for novice players to learn more tricks.

    * Duncan " Pulse" Yo-Yo: Not only the best light-up yo-yo on the market, but the Pulse™ is a high-quality, perfectly balanced, ball-bearing yo-yo that is actually unique, and affordable. New lighting technology offers increased color changing lights and patterns with each second of increased spin time. It turns a standard 2-handed performance into a fantastic show of light and color!

    * Duncan "ProYo" Yo-Yo: This yoyo was originally designed by Playmaxx toys but was eventually bought by Duncan. This ProYo is the same exact yoyo as the ProYo II, but with the Duncan logo. It features a wooden replaceable fixed axle along with a take apart design to get rid of those nasty knots. As one of the greatest beginner looping yoyos (experts use this as well) for the incredible price, this yoyo is bound to stay in the yoyoing community for a long time. 

    * Duncan Trick Book:  Updated with Freehand (counterweight) tricks, the Duncan Yo-Yo trick book includes over 60 tricks. Artist Li Shyu lays it out in 60 pages of fun and learning. Written by National Yo-Yo Master, Steve Brown!



    * Duncan "String Tricks, Volume 1 CD-Rom": Watch video on your computer to learn new tricks. Features Steve Brown!

    * Extra String: 100% Cotton Yo-Yo String. Pack of 3

             THIS KIT IS A $30.00 VALUE FOR ONLY $20.00!
